        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="weight-methodology">Development of weightings methodology</h2>
            <div class="govuk-grid-row">
                <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
                    <p>The Unified Tiering Model (UTM) requires weightings to feed other organisational tools such as the Workload Measurement Tool (WMT).
                        (Current Kainos WMT will be replaced by MoJ WMT by Dec 2021)
                    </p><br/>
                    <p>Plan is to move beyond dated probation modelling (used in the NPS Interim Tiering Model) and take a new approach using a
                        renewed activity-based methodology (utilising learning from the OMiC model).
                    </p><br/>
                    <strong>2-phase approach to be taken:</strong>
                    <ul class="govuk-list--bullet">
                        <li>Phase 1: To facilitate launch of UTM in April 21, will utilise current ITM weightings methodology with additional logic
